<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_815b95f4-12a3-405d-b360-2949ec359dcf" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><sptc>B5D8</sptc><title id="_2efc6cc4-0458-4cc0-8939-7a81c2b599f2">Cooling tower water service</title><archive-num>2019: NSW B5.501</archive-num><subclause id="_a0b30e63-ee8a-443d-9508-4e0efcff7420" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_cc1909fa-b3e4-4b8e-9493-e4e394209ee8">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Water systems permanently attached to cooling towers backflow prevention shall be positioned so that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_0dcec08c-af37-4c20-bf19-97589ffba805">cooling tower air gap must be measured from the rim of the cooling tower basin; and</li><li id="_fb06d6af-21d6-4f5e-b811-febc19243a16">if a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1250_0.7.0.xml#_762d6a54-e28c-400b-b9c5-5fceac019a05" id="_e9231372-7e61-48f3-8438-fed12f5bf215" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drinking water</xref> service to the cooling tower passes through the basin, the service pipe must be provided with a double wall protection; and</li><li id="_2c668f38-a0be-446c-b6bb-589ad3dffc92">if a fast fill connection is required, the fast fill line shall terminate externally to the unit, with an air gap over either the basin or a tundish.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_34d1692c-dc3a-4dbb-b321-46a4662371ef"><callout-type ncc-info-type="notes"/><p>See <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/7793_0.5.0.xml#_c68c514b-73ac-4137-8c5f-79ce965c12af" id="_215b83dc-2cf0-4e39-a89c-3336c1d6f4a0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="image-reference">NSW Figure B5D7</xref> for typical cooling tower connections.</p><image-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/7793_0.5.0.xml" id="_c68c514b-73ac-4137-8c5f-79ce965c12af" variation="NSW"><num/><title id="_89a8e8b1-1580-406d-81b3-4d00d1a8000b"/></image-reference></callout></clause>